item.title: CVE-2023-0369|2024-08-02T05:10:55.623Z -- unknown -- gotowp
item.description: The GoToWP WordPress plugin through 5.1.1 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
